        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="发布jar包到远程仓库"><a href="#发布jar包到远程仓库" class="headerlink" title="发布jar包到远程仓库"></a>发布jar包到远程仓库</h2><p>注意：</p><ol><li>如果 <code>gt-main-26.1.jar</code> 没有 POM 文件，Maven 可能会尝试查找 <code>org.geotools:library:pom:26.1</code> 但失败。你可以强制 Maven 自动生成 POM</li><li>jar所在目录不要再maven仓库下</li><li>也可以用此命令发布插件等</li></ol><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mvn deploy:deploy-file \</span><br><span class="line">  -Dfile=&quot;D:/xx/gt-main-<span class="number">26</span>.<span class="number">1</span>.jar&quot; \</span><br><span class="line">  -DgroupId=org.geotools \</span><br><span class="line">  -DartifactId=gt-main \</span><br><span class="line">  -Dversion=<span class="number">26</span>.<span class="number">1</span> \</span><br><span class="line">  -Dpackaging=jar \</span><br><span class="line">  -Durl=http://xx/artifactory/sw-gi-release \</span><br><span class="line">  -DrepositoryId=sw-release \</span><br><span class="line">  -DgeneratePom=true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
